column5: My group and I are heading back to Beteau Lake June 30th for Pike-O-Rama, just wondering if anyone else is fishing in the Nakina area this year and what outfitter you are going with? Cheers WW
Is this trip with Eddie North ?
Goodluck!  Johnson Silver Minnow with a big Kalins grub on the back was always the ticket for me when fishing up there
It is Eddies camp however Eddie is no longer the owner, he sold last year to Chris Lewis.

The only ones!  Although I was at Bass Pro yesterday stocking up for my trip and couldn't find the real big ones I like. Pro tip, some gorilla glue on the shaft of the hook to keep those plastics from being ripped off
